text: Bashkibash () is a rural locality (a selo) in Yalgyz-Naratsky Selsoviet, Tatyshlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 252 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 40 km from Verkhniye Tatyshly, 6 km from Yalgyz-Narat. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tatyshlinsky District
title: Bashkibash
